headline: Ross Stores (ROST) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know

headline: 3 Consumer Stocks with Solid Fundamentals
summary: Retailers are evolving to meet the expectations of modern, tech-savvy shoppers. Still, secular trends are working against their favor as e-commerce continues to take share from brick and mortars. This puts retail stocks in a tough spot, and over the past six months, the industry’s 20.3% gain has trailed the S&P 500 by 2.6 percentage points.
